  "title": "Monthly Treeverse Update #8",
  "link": "https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-8",
  "date": "2024-03-31T20:22:35.278Z",
  "content": "<div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\"><blockquote><p><span>An update on </span><a href=\"https://www.treeverse.net/\" rel=\"\">Treeverse</a><span>. A look at our development and art team progress. We will be posting monthly for you to follow along the development of </span><a href=\"https://www.treeverse.net/\" rel=\"\">Treeverse</a><span>, so make sure you subscribe!</span></p></blockquote><div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\"><div class=\"container-IpPqBD\"><form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" class=\"form form-M5sC90\" novalidate=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/end-claim-is-now-live\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-8\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-8\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\"><div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\"><div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative flexAuto-Bzdrdy pc-reset\"><input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\"></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button></div><div id=\"error-container\"></div></form><div class=\"animationWrapper-QRL6aQ\"></div></div></div></div><div><hr></div><p>This month we hit a milestone. We released our first combat trailer, all in-game footage with everything created in-house! It did very well publicly receiving immense support and attracting more people to Treeverse. Make no mistake, this is small in comparison to what we are building over the next few years. We are so excited to build in public with all of you.</p><p><span>To view a HD version of the Trailer, it‚Äôs </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pA31rxn3hYM&amp;t=5s\" rel=\"\">available on our new YouTube channel</a><span> - be sure to subscribe!</span></p><h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Concept Art Update<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"¬ßconcept-art-update\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/61845021/concept-art-update\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h2><p>Over the last month, including the Combat Trailer that released yesterday, we‚Äôve amassed 550K+ views on Treeverse footage and millions of impressions on Twitter! And people love the art direction of Treeverse; as you can see the footage is a culmination of the art we‚Äôve shown across the last few months.</p><p><strong>Some words from Scott, our Art Director:</strong></p><ul><li><p><span>‚ÄúFor the month of July, the art team has been focusing on raising the health of the project. After creating the trailer and the demo, we are focusing on cleaning up the structures of the art assets, naming, and file standardization. This may sound boring, but it is an important step when building a large-scale game like Treeverse.</span><br><br><span>The concept team are continuing to work hard on building the world, we are now starting to explore some interior space. The approach will be entirely different to what we had before, with a darker and more atmospheric tone (Image below). The art team will make sure we have a variety of environments to make dungeon runs more interesting. </span><br><br><span>The UI team is working to lock down our in-game aesthetic as well as some transition pages. As the art style of Treeverse becomes more solidified, the UI team is also able to be more precise with their decision choices to match what we see inside the game.‚Äù</span></p></li></ul><div data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://twitter.com/TheTreeverse/status/1553457313620656134&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;FIRST LOOK: Treeverse Combat Trailer üå±‚öîÔ∏è &quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;TheTreeverse&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Treeverse (üå±)&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;Sat Jul 30 19:07:40 +0000 2022&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[{&quot;img_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/upload/w_728,c_limit/l_twitter_play_button_rvaygk,w_120/ckptwxi2hneoiqr8uipv&quot;,&quot;link_url&quot;:&quot;https://t.co/XKmJG5gVaC&quot;,&quot;alt_text&quot;:null}],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;retweet_count&quot;:607,&quot;like_count&quot;:2766,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:{},&quot;video_url&quot;:&quot;https://video.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/1553456931368538114/pu/vid/640x360/I1JIFR7i20Nr55f7.mp4?tag=12&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}\